{"id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0018", "text": "願你沒有嫌它 穿不破", "structure": {"line_index": 18, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 5, 0, 3, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyun6", "nei5", "mut6", "jau5", "jim4", "taa1", "cyun1", "bat1", "po3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嫌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "它", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "穿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不破", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "501", "artists": ["梁漢文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3302", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0017", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0019", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0019", "text": "還可以 着什麼 每個身軀差距無多", "structure": {"line_index": 19, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 5, 2, 2, 3, 5, 4, 3, 3, 3, 5, 0, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waan4", "ho2", "ji5", "zoek6", "sam6", "mo1", "mui5", "go3", "san1", "keoi1", "caa1", "keoi5", "mou4", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "每個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "身軀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "差距", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "501", "artists": ["梁漢文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3302", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0018", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0020", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0020", "text": "有幾多百萬男孩亦是着它 怎會得我", "structure": {"line_index": 20, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 9, 3, 4, 2, 0, 0, 2, 2, 2, 3, 9, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jau5", "gei2", "do1", "baak3", "maan6", "naam4", "haai4", "jik6", "si6", "zoek6", "taa1", "zam2", "dak1", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幾多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "百萬", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "男孩", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "它", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "501", "artists": ["梁漢文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3302", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0019", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0021", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0021", "text": "如今你 愛什麼 到處撫摸找到什麼", "structure": {"line_index": 21, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 4, 2, 3, 4, 9, 9, 9, 4, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "gam1", "nei5", "oi3", "sam6", "mo1", "dou3", "fu2", "mo2", "zaau2", "dou3", "sam6", "mo1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如今", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到處", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撫摸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "501", "artists": ["梁漢文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3302", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0020", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0022", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0022", "text": "但你在途上不要認錯", "structure": {"line_index": 22, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 0, 3, 4, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "nei5", "zoi6", "tou4", "bat1", "jiu3", "jing6", "co3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "途上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "認錯", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "501", "artists": ["梁漢文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3302", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0021", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0023", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0023", "text": "被擦白的藍色 只得我", "structure": {"line_index": 23, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 2, 3, 0, 3, 9, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bei6", "caat3", "baak6", "dik1", "laam4", "sik1", "zi2", "dak1", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "被", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "擦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "白", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "藍色", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "501", "artists": ["梁漢文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3302", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0022", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5rGJ5paH_MzMwMg_0024", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
